 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361aa430f46b7196556d0ff94b09b5d2aabd6c84","tid":41024,"uid":47473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>落大街，有糖水有公仔面<br />\n個撈面好撚大個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n坐街邊果檔?<br />\n幾好食，不過好多小強"},{"pid":"e23fed4a63cbedefe648f4b17ec0f2ce8f8d46c5","tid":41024,"uid":47473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:22:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個成日ff如果拆咗港燈嗰度然後將個商場擴建就正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就好似太古城個商場嗰啲咁啦<br />\n<br />\n而家真係乜柒都啖好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起酒店丫"},{"pid":"9c1d907fd0c2d2b6d17d6c09e60ca016fb6ca46a","tid":41024,"uid":17405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>落大街，有糖水有公仔面<br />\n個撈面好撚大個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n坐街邊果檔?<br />\n幾好食，不過好多小強</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係夜晚成個鴨脷洲除左呢度又真係無野食<br />\n<br />\n我晚晚買宵夜返屋企食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0853700e69e6bfe8bdaac793f49b82c4539411fc","tid":41024,"uid":37575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個成日ff如果拆咗港燈嗰度然後將個商場擴建就正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就好似太古城個商場嗰啲咁啦<br />\n<br />\n而家真係乜柒都啖好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起酒店丫</blockquote><br />\n唔係banned咗好耐喇咩？"},{"pid":"23b388db3e57d515b16ad206c4e69441d2ddb3c5","tid":41024,"uid":15740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:54:28.000Z","msg":"香港仔都沒乜"},{"pid":"50700c3ee0b94138212968256766e7da0157b75f","tid":41024,"uid":35923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"