":17405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，住左海怡十幾年，一直都有同感，以前有food court 都好少少，而家乜鳩都冇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以依家晚飯宵夜都係落大街算，行路落都係15分鐘，都唔使揸車"},{"pid":"9d217e1ecd254630460bbf787e498e852c26ce68","tid":41024,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:04:28.000Z","msg":"香港仔乜都冇呀Diu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03247420e3576f19a2abcc30ce5341d69c68d13","tid":41024,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:09:07.000Z","msg":"青衣美景先係Boss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5f32df4dae5ac0f7fbbc247ef6516a35ccdc07","tid":41024,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:28:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個成日ff如果拆咗港燈嗰度然後將個商場擴建就正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就好似太古城個商場嗰啲咁啦<br />\n<br />\n而家真係乜柒都啖好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起酒店丫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學東隅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68550851219a7c61cdedf4d38ffdddae76f74657","tid":41024,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個成日ff如果拆咗港燈嗰度然後將個商場擴建就正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就好似太古城個商場嗰啲咁啦<br />\n<br />\n而家真係乜柒都啖好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日諗人地太古城啲樓舊咁多<br />\n但個商場就靚過海怡嗰個咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人地一開始就要爭成個東區塊餅, 地方大上蓋有樓有office, 隔離係康怡吉芝島, 競爭勁好多"},{"pid":"b6c82ef774667ba32ae016815db930a2c4f2c667","tid":41024,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:37:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>細個成日ff如果拆咗港燈嗰度然後將個商場擴建就正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就好似太古城個商場嗰啲咁啦<br />\n<br />\n而家真係乜柒都啖好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起酒店丫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學東隅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n海怡設計啲樓圍住晒, 酒店會有更明顯私隱問題</blockquote>"},{"pid":"12b0b5a2a734b7152e67be9653fa6a9a7de47cbd","tid":41024,"uid":57261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:53:48.000Z","msg":"住左8年，而家搬左<br />\n每次番到去見到西商場都唔知講咩好<br />\n<br />\n話時話好耐之前地下果層賣玩具遊戲機既係咪搬左去東商場？"}]}